### ─── 1. View Your Matches ───

### View all your matches (perfect matches show up first)
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### View only your perfect matches (direct skill exchange)
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches?type=perfect
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### View only your partial matches (requires credits)
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches?type=partial
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Filter matches to only show tech skills
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches?category=tech
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Filter matches to only show beginners
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches?level=beginner
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Sort matches by the other user's rating (highest first)
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches?sort=rating
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Sort matches by the number of sessions the other user has completed
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches?sort=sessions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### View matches using pagination (Page 1, 5 items)
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches?page=1&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Combine multiple filters (perfect tech matches, sorted by rating)
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches?type=perfect&category=tech&sort=rating&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Test: Try to use a wrong match type filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches?type=superMatch
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Test: Try to use a wrong sort parameter
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches?sort=alphabetical
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ─── 2. View a Specific Match ───

### View details of a specific match
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches/{{matchId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Test: Try to view a match that doesn't exist
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Test: Try to view a match that belongs to someone else
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches/e492ee4c-99a6-462a-9d43-241d431cb669
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ─── 3. Admin Tools ───

### Force the system to recalculate all matches immediately
POST {{baseUrl}}/matches/recalculate
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Test: Try to recalculate matches using a normal user account
POST {{baseUrl}}/matches/recalculate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
